    "This is because the LLMs employed in this work are designed to process textual inputs.",
    "Thus, the tasks heavily depend on the accuracy of the text conversion process used (e.g., OCR).",
    "However, even the best text conversion techniques still struggle to achieve 100% accurate text conversions from documents such as PDFs and images.",
    "To deal with this challenge, it is recommended to further advance text extraction techniques to improve the accuracy and quality.",
    "Integrating computer vision techniques or machine learning algorithms could be a potential area."
